  m_text: 'You must make your way to the cabin in the forest to meet your friend.


    Watch
    out for the creatures that lurk nearby.....


    Your friend holds all the answers
    to defeat each enemy.


    Work with them to survive the night, but don''t let
    your phone run out of battery.


    Click to interact

    Press P to open your
    phone


    If you use the phone too much it will die, so make the right choices!


    Not
    everything is what it seems.....'
